ocket-scienti%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarvin+Hewitt\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\">Burton, Sarah (2001). <i>Impostors: Six Kinds of Liar</i>. Penguin. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-14-028250-5\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-14-028250-5\">0-14-028250-5</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Impostors%3A+Six+Kinds+of+Liar&amp;rft.pub=Penguin&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.isbn=0-14-028250-5&amp;rft.aulast=Burton&amp;rft.aufirst=Sarah&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarvin+Hewitt\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,857410,00.html\">The Compulsion.</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Time_magazine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Time magazine\">Time magazine</a>. March 15, 1954</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=PFQEAAAAMBAJ&amp;pg=PA57&amp;lpg=PA57&amp;dq=Honest+career+for+Ph%28ony%29D&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=kXxlxyHO8n&amp;sig=7HYwWT2xi96tfllc1FgqHG5XQtE&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=NkuLS8WxKYG1tgf8oMSvDw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CAgQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=Honest%20career%20for%20Ph%28ony%29D&amp;f=false\">Honest career for Ph(ony)D: brilliant hoaxer Marvin Hewitt becomes a respected engineer.</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Life_magazine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Life magazine\">Life magazine</a>. January 21, 1957, pp.&#160;57\u201382.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1238\nCached time: 20180908000457\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time us